Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:52.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,扛住. 看着点, 小心点.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. Watch it, watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,扛住, 扛住, 扛住了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, hold it, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了. 好了.\N- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Got it. Got it.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,用肩扛,\N把它扛在肩上.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your shoulder,\Nput it on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:03.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小心看路.\N- 小心看路.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Watch the step.\N- Watch the step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点, 慢点.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要搬到那里,\N就说一声.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you need some help down there,\Nsay something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小心点.\N- 继续走.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Watch it.\N- Keep it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别走太快了.\N- 慢点来.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't go too fast.\N- Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那样就对了, 继续走.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你踩到我脚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me in the foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小心车.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 车就在这儿.\N- 好咧.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The car's right here.\N- That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你小心看路.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 不是吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳提?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rusty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳提姓什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was Rusty's last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马吉.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomasky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:51.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他带我进乐团.\N做巡回乐队管理员.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me in with the band.\Nl'm a roadie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们来双峰镇\N干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nin Twin Peaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来刀河这儿\N演出的,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to play a gig\Nin Knife River,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但一个轮胎爆了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a tire on the van crapped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你遇见了一个人.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 这家伙--\N这家伙从林子里走出来,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this guy--\NThis guy came out of the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像大脚怪，野人之类的,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like Bigfoot or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他穿这一套怪异的衣服.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's wearing a weird suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:13.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们和他聊了一会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we talked to him for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:19.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后他说他那儿有酒,\N唔, 问我们要不要来点.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said he had some brew,\Nyou know, would we like some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳提就跟着他去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Rusty went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就再也没见过他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't see him after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要通知\N纳提的父母.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to get in touch\Nwith Rusty's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:33.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他恨他的父母.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hated his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:40.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直住在摩西湖他叔叔那儿\N直到我们打算--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's staying with his uncle\Nin Moses Lake until we were gonna--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打算离开.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were gonna move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们原来还想着去洛杉几的.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were gonna move to L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚! 看着点儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My foot! Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他又把一个兵卒干掉了, 哈里,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken another pawn, Harry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他没有预告我们这一步.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't tell us his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔\N玩过界了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle's\Nplaying off the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早啊, 露西.\N- 早, 杜鲁门警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morning, Lucy.\N- Morning, Sheriff Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早, 露西.\N- 库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morning, Lucy.\N- Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长,\N豪克警官在你的办公室.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Hawk is in your office,\Nsheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他和一个人在里面\N这人我之前没见过的,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with somebody\Nl've never seen before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来真的很伤心,\N豪克正请他吃早餐安慰他.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he looks really sad,\Nso Hawk is feeding him breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事, 露西?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对于拯救我们的星球\N你知道多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know\Nabout saving our planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这里面有数不清的问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know it's in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:49.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 通常\N我都心存太多疑虑.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, l'm taking fate\Ninto my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:53.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这次，我要\N自己掌握命运.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly because the suspense\Nis too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:57.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是父日. 父亲节.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is D-day. Dad Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:02.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,24小时内,\N我将会选择谁做我孩子的父亲.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln 24 hours,\Nl will choose the father of my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪·布伦南警官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Andy Brennan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:09.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或者服装推销员\N理查·揣眉.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or clothing salesman\NRichard Tremayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟双峰小姐比赛\N有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do\Nwith the Miss Twin Peaks contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:19.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想,\N父亲和钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-- l mean, we could use\Nthe money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都能用的上.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could also use a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要准备一篇关于\N拯救我们行星的演讲稿,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l have to make a speech\Nabout saving our planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个很棒的概念,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is a great concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然一点\N头绪都没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l have no idea\Nhow to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:37.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒认为人们在珍珠湖\N钓鱼的时候，必须停止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do know that people have got to stop\Nsinking their beer cans in Pearl Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:39.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,往湖里丢啤酒罐的行为.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they're fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒罐.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beer cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:46.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而泡沫塑料则是永不死身，只要你还活着\N一天，它都不会被分解掉的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Styrofoam never dies\Nfor as long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:50.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 兰迪, 欧蕊回来了没?\N- 没, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Randy, has Audrey returned?\N- No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有她消息吗?\N- 没有, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No messages from her?\N- No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能派个人上去\N帮我拿袋子吗? 麻烦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you send someone up\Nfor my bags, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保险公司\N给我寄了好多表格资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The insurance companies\Nsend me so many forms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:29.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我得了心脏病\N好像能让他们振奋不已似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l could get a heart attack\Njust lifting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好的很.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至于你心里面想什么\N倒是值得你去担心.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's what's in your heart\Nyou should be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你有理由\N去怀疑我.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that l have given you\Nreason to doubt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:48.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在唯一的兴趣\N就是为大家做好事.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l am only interested in doing\Nthe right thing for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就离艾琳远点.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay away from Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要谎言还存在，我就办不到.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as the lie survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼, 你是怎么了，本. 事情没那么简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Ben. lt's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是相信你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你做好事的欲望\N鼓掌欢呼.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l applaud your desire\Nto do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但善良对于你来说--\N简直就像一颗定时炸弹.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But goodness in you is--\Nlt's like a time bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把好好的生活给毁了\N这样做没什么善良可言.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing good\Nabout ruined lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:19.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个过程的确艰难\N又令人困顿.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is a confusing\Nand difficult process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我必须继续下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l must continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了, 伟.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:34.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 杰克, 进来吧.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jack, come on in.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识伟·海沃德?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Will Hayward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:39.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,认识, 你好. 我见过你女儿.\N她真可爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello. l've met your daughter.\NShe's a lovely girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:44.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 我该回\N办公室去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, should be getting back\Nto my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又见到你真好, 庄.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you again, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 悠着点, 拜托了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, be careful, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been looking for Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她应该马上就到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be back any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 我得走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, l gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们说话这当口上\N他们已经在帮我的飞机加油了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gassing up the jet\Nas we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 既然你这么赶\N就先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can call her\Nwhen you get to wherever it is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以随时给她电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are in such a hurry to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的一个朋友--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了朋友, 他还是\N我的合伙人. --他被谋杀了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was more than a friend, he was\Na partner. --he's been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:43.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女生.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Female child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,母, 艾琳·海沃德.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, Eileen Hayward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女, 唐娜·玛丽.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter, Donna Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,父...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜? 唐娜, 你在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna? Donna, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了, 妈?\N- 豪克警官打电话来找你.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it, Mom?\N- Deputy Hawk is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说是紧要事.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 荷恩小姐, 有几个消息给你的.\N- 好极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ms. Horne, l have several messages.\N- Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我帮你拿吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll take that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的. 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员有事，\N想请你去警局见他.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper would like to see you\Nat the sheriff's station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 这, 我现在有好多事要做.\N今天下午吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, l have a lot of work to do.\NMaybe this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:54.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻要去. 急事.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now. lt's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你走了，那停止格斯伍计划怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Stop Ghostwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:04.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎样\N才能留着你?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am l supposed\Nto get ahold of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要更多时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个勇士死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brave man is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的朋友,\N我必须回去接替他的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend,\Nand l have to take his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算回来了, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't coming back, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒那些雨林烦事\N真该死.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this rainforest business\Nanyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有我，你也能应付过来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can handle this without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:25.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.\N我好怕，我好虚弱.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.\Nl'm afraid that l'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩, 虚弱?\N谁会信啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne, weak?\Nl find that hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为善良仁慈而奋斗, 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strive for goodness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先说最艰难的事实.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the hardest truth first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽力而为吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你所能做到的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you really can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我很抱歉\N欧蕊不在.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm sorry\Nthat Audrey wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你帮我\N转交个东西给她.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to give her\Nsomething for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她我--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her l--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给她就好了, 你会照办吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it to her, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去查查看这些符号\N和收割时分表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See if any of these symbols\Nhave to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或者古代历法\N有没有联系.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,harvest schedules\Nor ancient calendars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找出任何相关的古怪术语.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for any curious nomenclature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了, 长官.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好好干, 卡皮.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Cappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 少校. 战况如何?\N- 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Major. How goes the battle?\N- Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 库珀探员.\N- 少校, 你看起来很疲倦.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agent Cooper.\N- Major, you look bushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 我花了一晚上终于搞到了\N蓝皮书项目的档案，仔细看了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l spent the night obtaining and\Nperusing the Project Blue Book files
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我读完云顿·厄尔的相关资料后.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regarding Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我发现自己难以入眠.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l found it impossible to sleep after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你收集到什么情报?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you gleaned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔曾是我们中\N最棒最聪明的一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle was the best\Nand brightest among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，当我们的注意力\N转移到外太空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when our attention\Nturned from outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是围绕着双峰镇\N树林这一带区域,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the wooded areas\Nsurrounding Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就开始变得神不守舍.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he became destructively obsessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:46.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔的行为表现的过分激动\N而且经常鬼鬼祟祟的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle acted in an overzealous\Nand secretive manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不听命令，私自行动,\N最终以暴力告终了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessive of his assignments,\Nfinally violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他被开除出项目了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was removed from the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在档案馆找到这个的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l found this in the project archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这些-- 这些邪恶的男巫,\N他们被称作, 德帕族,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These-- These evil sorcerers,\Ndugpas, they're called,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:05.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}邪恶令他们不断的培育出邪恶,\N除此没别的了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they cultivate evil for the sake of evil,\Nnothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}为了黑暗\N他们以黑暗代表自己{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They express themselves\Nin darkness for darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}而不受任何动机影响.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without leavening motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:17.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在, 这，这份对黑暗炽热又强烈的忠贞\N允许他们进入一个秘密的地方{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this-- This ardent purity\Nallows them to access a secret place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一个能让他们培育邪恶的程序\N将呈几何级增长的地方,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the cultivation of evil proceeds\Nin exponential fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:25.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在那里, 邪恶的能量\N就可以得到大幅促进.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with it, the furtherance\Nof evil's resulting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:30.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这块能量园是有形的\N正因如此, 它是可以被找到, 并进入的{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place of power is tangible\Nand as such, it can be found, entered
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}或许能以某种形式\N对其加以利用.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and perhaps utilized\Nin some fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}德帕族给它起了\N很多名字,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dugpas have many names\Nfor it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:41.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但其中最主要的名字是--\N守夜门.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but chief among them is the--\Nls the Black Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你们不信我, 是吧?\N你们以为我疯了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me, do you?\NYou think l'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}以为我工作过度了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}算了吧，滚开.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:59.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们, 当云顿·厄尔\N抵达双峰镇,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, when Windom Earle\Narrived in Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为\N他是为报复我.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l assumed\Nhe had come for vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我失算了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他暗中将自己混入\N我们所关爱的人当中.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has insinuated himself\Ninto the lives of people l care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后又滥杀无辜.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has murdered innocents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,目的就在于转移注意力\N是我们疲于奔命应战.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has engaged us in subterfuge\Nand red herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就不会特别留意一条漏网之鱼了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fish l don't particularly care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但所有这些动作\N都不过是幌子罢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all of these acts\Nare merely camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这背后，原来他自始至终\N想要的是:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been after something else\Nall along:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:26.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,守夜门.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:33.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们, 我们必须找出,\N这守夜门, 到底和那个什么关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fellas, we need to find out what this,\Nthe Black Lodge, has to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信\N这之间有联系?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe\Nthere's a connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:40.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔相信, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle does, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了. 哈里, 我们一定要把这些\N档案彻底看个遍.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Harry, we're gonna go\Nthrough these files from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:56.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,卡皮, 我要你把一切有关\N德帕族的事都挖出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cappy, l want you to dig up\Neverything you can about the dugpas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少校,\N我想你最好去睡一觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major,\Nl think you'd better hit the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以舒服地伸个懒腰了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could use a good stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:03.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许在林子里散散步\N有助于我清醒头脑.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a walk in the woods\Nto clear my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意.\N别忘了给林子里的鸟带点面包屑.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.\NDon't forget the bread crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我们开始吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗, 里欧, 哥伦布\N发现的唯一 一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Leo, the only thing\Nthat Columbus discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他所失去的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was that he was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:25.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀和他的同党们\N还不够老道呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper and the gang\Nhaven't even left the snide yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们所不知的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know something they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道某些小戴尔\N几乎不会怀疑的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know something young Dale\Nmerely suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝皮书项目.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Blue Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小人物,\N盲目乐观的田凫鸟.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little men,\Npewits loaded with optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有的威慑力就那么一丁点了\N这简直就是一种鼓励啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a deterrent so slight\Nit was practically encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过有几个问题\N我倒想问布里格斯少校.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet l would like to ask Major Briggs\Na question or three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:50.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把他那粒小光头好好打磨抛光\N看着它如此闪闪发亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polish up that bald nub of his\Nand see what shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:59.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 也许, 我们俩该出去冒冒险，\N舒展一下筋骨了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, Leo, we too\Nshould venture out for a good stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:02.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和少校重聚蓝皮书项目\N那不很有趣嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be fun to have\Na Project Blue Book reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,酒, 芝士, 畅谈旧时,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wine, cheese, talk about old times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再次换来过去那风花雪月\N充满奇闻轶事的欢乐时光.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trade hilarious anecdotes\Nof the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:13.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想我生命中的碎石瓦砾\N能为布里格斯的人生增添点风味.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder what amongst my detritus\Nl can use to spice up Briggs' life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 别傻站着了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, stop dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这样站在外面,就麻烦了\N鸽子会来戳你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you were outside,\Nyou'd have trouble with pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"那是我们拯救那些树木的\N唯一办法.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''And that's the only way\Nwe're ever going to save the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候要为我们的环境\N积极行动起来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's time to stand up and kick some butt\Nfor our environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:40.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在它为时已晚之前，为了我们大家."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it's too late for all of us.''
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,写的真美, 一字不差.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's beautiful, letter-perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道用\N"积极行动"好不好.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know about\Nthe ''kick butt'' part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,改用"战斗"怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about ''fight''?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候要站起来\N为我们的环境而战斗了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's time to stand up\Nand fight for our environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个词好多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 我一直在想.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, l've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 波比, 我懂, 我懂, 我懂.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bobby, l know, l know, l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:07.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 演讲算双--\N- 别提什么比赛了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The speech counts double--\N- Forget about the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想关于我们的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been thinking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:18.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道最近一直没有\N给你太多关心.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that l have not been paying\Nthe right kind of attention to you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我忙着跟荷恩先生混.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got busy with Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始穿起套装, 好了,\N然后我突然觉得走路也神气活现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l started wearing suits, okay,\Nand suddenly l'm walking around
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,趾高气扬起来了，好像我比\N谁都重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like l'm more important\Nthan everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前的确一副穷酸相.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty crummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:38.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 我想你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, l've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我怀念我们在一起\N做过的所有事.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've missed all the things\Nwe used to do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:50.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我看见你亲那个\N家伙时...脑袋就炸轰了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l saw you kissing\Nthat guy...something snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时几乎快气晕过去了,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was like my brain rolled over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:59.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我这才看到原来这一切\N对我有多么特别.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l could see all the stuff\Nthat was special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切是如此重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the stuff that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你, 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you, Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以后都能\N那样过.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l wanna spend my time\Nwith that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 你知道么,\N如果你可以的话,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, you know,\Nif that's okay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意这样做, 你懂吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like to do that, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真幸运.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员的电话.\N他有事找你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper's on the line.\NHe needs to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:44.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快点, 雪莉, 他说是要事.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Shelly, he says it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我有天大的好消息.\N- 是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l've got great news.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:12.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是诺玛·詹宁斯\N和理查·揣眉将会加入评委组.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's going to be Norma Jennings\Nand Richard Tremayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,揣眉是第三位评委.\N这次十拿九稳了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremayne is the third judge.\Nlt's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 现在, 我必须要确保.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, l have to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝, 我必须确保\N我会赢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, l have to be sure\Nl'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:26.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我的上帝, 这家伙是英国人\N或者是巴哈马人什么的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God, this guy's British\Nor Bahamian or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他会为你的魅力而拜倒.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's bound to fall for your charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:34.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会想个办法\N把你们俩弄到一块, 单独.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find some way\Nto get you two together, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢,\N你故意穿一件有裂缝的衣服.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then,\Nyou put on a dress with a slit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:41.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 那条大裂缝一直\N裂到西雅图那儿去.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the slit cut halfway\Nup to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在之后呢, 渐渐偎依过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, nestle in real close to him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当他一眼看到\N这双美腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when he gets a look\Nat those gams
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:57.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和闻到洒在你身上的\N法国香水，那他...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and smells that French perfume\Ndripping off you and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:04.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...就会开始\N迷失在这双棕色眼睛里了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...becomes lost\Nin those brown eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 好了. 好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,停下, 你这小母狐, 你.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you vixen, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我快受不了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们不干脆私奔算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we just elope and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:21.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不. 现在不行, 直到我赢了为止, 亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Now, not until l've won, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那时，只有到那时,\N我才会嫁给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, and only then,\Nl will marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 你好苛刻哦, 亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're so strict, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个遭罪市长啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l am the blasted mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 乖, 宝贝, 来这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now, baby, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们每个人\N都以古怪的方式.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of you received\Na piece of this poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,收到一片诗,\N还连带着这个邀请.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each in a curious manner,\Nalong with this invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都去了公路吧,\N但没有人出现.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all went to the Roadhouse,\Nnobody showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:56.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们最近有接触过\N一个陌生人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any of you had contact recently\Nwith a stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:02.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有留下什么印象，比如神经兮兮的,\N风度优雅，又或是有的莫名其妙的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who struck you as peculiar,\Npersonable or just plain puzzling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:07.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 见过一个生人\N他说是我爸爸的一个朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there was this strange guy who\Nsaid he was a friend of my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到诗那天,\N还收到10美金小费，就放在咖啡杯旁.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same day l got the poem,\Nl got a $1 0 tip for a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那很不常见.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你, 我有次在图书馆里碰见了\N一个风趣的老头儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there was a funny old guy\Nat the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他要我\N为他念这首诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me\Nto read the poem to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,3个都有.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 靠近点仔细看.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这笔迹\N眼熟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this handwriting\Nlook familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是里欧的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Leo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:38.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们每个人\N每天来警察局报告2次.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want each of you to check in\Nwith the sheriff twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,早上9点,\N晚上9点各一次.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine o'clock in the morning,\N9:00 at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们的父母\N全天候知道你们的所在地.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want your parents\Nto know your whereabouts at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你走路上学,\N还是开车去上班,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk to school,\Nyou drive to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都确保你们\N不要独自一人.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure\Nthat you do not do so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:57.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我\N当我告诉你们要小心时.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me\Nwhen l tell you to be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的情形很危险.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会欣赏\N德帕族的, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would've appreciated\Nthe dugpas, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,远古男巫对邪恶的忠贞不二.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient sorcerers bent on evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,颇像印度教朝拜者对\N暴虐黑暗女神迦梨的朝圣.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather like the Kali worshippers\Nin lndia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告诉你,\N又是一帮出色的小丑.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another fine bunch of zanies,\Nl can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一日三餐, 以血为生.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood for breakfast, blood for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是好时光啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:39.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雪莉.\N- 很好啊, 里欧, 你还记得.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shelly.\N- Very good, Leo, you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,浅薄庸俗的小娼妇.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tawdry little trollop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这事我只和你说好了, 小老弟,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me, old boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:49.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子对婚姻的忠诚度\N有相当摩登的看法.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your wife has some\Nfairly modern views on marital fidelity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这不要紧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她仍然适合做皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is still fit for a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:58.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会哀悼她的死吗, 里欧?\N我很怀疑哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mourn her passing, Leo?\Nl doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她的死, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her death, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉即将迎来超度.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly's imminent demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会非常简单, 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's very simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:12.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉在双峰小姐中胜出,\N然后死去.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly wins Miss Twin Peaks,\NShelly dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你愿意帮一把.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'd like to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉. 不要.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好家伙, 你手上拿的什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good God, what have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:25.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别, 里欧, 我求你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Leo, l'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:29.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 求求你. 饶了我吧, 里欧.\N- 爱雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l prithee. Have mercy, Leo.\N- Love Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:58.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或多或少, 我们都会对傻子有点好感.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all love's fools, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你会吸取教训的, 正如,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will learn, as l have,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:03.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨对我的价值.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the value of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:07.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:33.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨, 爸爸.\N- 哦, 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Daddy.\N- Oh, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欢迎到家, 小蜜糖.\N- 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Welcome home, honey.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早就回来了\N但库珀探员有事找我, 所以就...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got back this morning but\NAgent Cooper needed to see me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:41.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:43.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有个变态给我送了一首诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some creep sent me a poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话去杰克房间,\N但他不在那儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l tried to call Jack's room,\Nbut he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:50.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道他去哪儿了?\N- 欧蕊, 你不在的时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you know where he is?\N- Audrey, while you were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:54.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我突发奇想，有了一个极不可思议的点子.\N- 是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l had the most incredible brainstorm.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:59.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,停止格斯伍的活动\N需要一个代言人.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:24:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stop Ghostwood movement\Nneeds a spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:03.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个能见度高的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with a highly visible profile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:07.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能激励我们的社团\N并肩作战的形象.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be able to inspire\Nour community to action.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:09.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸, 杰克在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, where's Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这你能做到, 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:15.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,作为双峰小姐出现,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Miss Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:19.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你就能借此公众平台\N成为那个代言人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could be that spokesperson\Nand you could use your public platform
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:23.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不, 爸.\N- 作为一个辩论环境问题的论坛.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, Dad.\N- as a forum for environmental debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:25.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 听我说, 你能做到的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, listen, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.64,0:24:28.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能把我们的信息\N带给人们.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you can take our message\Nto the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.74,0:24:34.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,\N庄·爵斯廷·维乐在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy,\Nwhere is John Justice Wheeler?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:39.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他走了.\N- 他要去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.22,0:24:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's gone.\N- Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:47.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西发生惨剧了\N要他立即回去处理.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some tragedy in Brazil\Ndemanded his immediate attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:52.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他给你留了一封信,\N在我这儿呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a letter for you,\Nl have it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:53.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:59.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他什么时候走的?\N- 几分钟之前出发去机场了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.48,0:24:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- When did he leave?\N- A few minutes ago to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.37,0:25:02.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊,\N那双峰小姐的事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.68,0:25:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey,\Nwhat about Miss Twin Peaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.46,0:25:04.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我迟点再和你商量这事儿,\N好么? 我保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.78,0:25:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll talk with you about this later,\Nokay? l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.82,0:25:08.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊. 欧蕊. 欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.15,0:25:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey. Audrey. Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.76,0:25:15.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西, 我看见你的脸了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.06,0:25:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie, l see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:18.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 兰迪.\N- 在.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.59,0:25:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Randy.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.56,0:25:21.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 算了. 你.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.86,0:25:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.31,0:25:22.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.57,0:25:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:25.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆货车. 开起来顺极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.14,0:25:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A truck. Runs like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.19,0:25:27.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了, 我们走.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.47,0:25:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.89,0:25:30.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等等. 噢, 抱歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.17,0:25:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Oh, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.73,0:25:34.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快点. 快点.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.08,0:25:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.71,0:25:40.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这, 符号表示时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.02,0:25:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the symbols suggest a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.94,0:25:42.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很明确.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.22,0:25:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.81,0:25:46.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么时间?\N- 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A time for what?\N- l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.35,0:25:49.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始我还以为是一个路标.\N也可能是个邀请信号.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.63,0:25:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first l thought it was a signpost.\NPerhaps it's an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.62,0:25:51.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者2者皆是.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.90,0:25:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.06,0:25:54.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少校在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.37,0:25:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the major?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:25:57.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在应该到了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:25:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:26:01.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 给布里格斯太太打个电话,\N看少校是否还在家里.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.64,0:26:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, give Mrs. Briggs a call,\Nsee if the major's home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.65,0:26:13.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在干嘛呢, 库?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.92,0:26:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Coop?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:17.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 在想\N安妮·伯本.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.65,0:26:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just thinking\Nabout Annie Blackburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.41,0:26:22.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,呀, 乖乖,\N我还不知道你也会走神.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.73,0:26:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bless your heart,\Nl've never known your mind to wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.51,0:26:25.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 哈里,\N我已经走神一整天了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Harry,\Nl've been feeling this way all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.09,0:26:30.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道么, 我如常工作,\N我头脑清晰而专注
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.43,0:26:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l proceed as usual,\Nmy mind clear and focused
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:37.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但突然间, 也不知从哪里冒出来的,\N我就看到她的脸和听到她的声音了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.37,0:26:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suddenly, out of nowhere,\Nl see her face and l hear her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.78,0:26:41.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很自然的, 我要努力调整自己,\N重新回到手头上的任务,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.08,0:26:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, l try to reorient myself,\Ncome back to the task at hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.79,0:26:44.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但那些影像仍逗留在脑海里.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.05,0:26:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the image remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.76,0:26:47.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时我确实觉得很晕眩.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.05,0:26:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes l actually feel dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.42,0:26:50.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱中的人\N都那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in love\Nis supposed to feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.87,0:26:53.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我的症状通常是\N得疟疾.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.19,0:26:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my symptoms suggest\Nthe onset of malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.09,0:26:56.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的一生中没有比这感觉更好的了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.39,0:26:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l've never felt better in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.11,0:27:00.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉, 哈里, 这听起来太傻了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.43,0:27:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Harry, that sounds foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.68,0:27:04.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 没有的事, 伙计, 这是幸运才对.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, man, it sounds lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.87,0:27:47.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}家, 家在此山中{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.21,0:27:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home, home on the range
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.45,0:27:51.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}鹿在哪里?\N羚羊在玩乐{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.78,0:27:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the deer\NAnd the antelope play
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.50,0:27:56.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那里难得听到\N令人沮丧的话语{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.78,0:27:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where seldom is heard\NA discouraging word
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.56,0:27:58.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊, 伟伯.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.86,0:27:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Wilbur.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.12,0:28:12.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}天空永远是万里无云{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.47,0:28:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the skies are not cloudy all day
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.02,0:28:20.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了, 小布里.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Briggsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.66,0:28:27.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.23,0:28:29.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来，终于\N有人给你作伴了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.49,0:28:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt looks like\Nyou've finally found your calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.93,0:28:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去参加没什么坏处啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.21,0:28:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't hurt to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.89,0:28:57.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许明年吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.21,0:28:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.25,0:29:01.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮, 全世界在外面.\N勇敢点，加入吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.58,0:29:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, there's a whole world out there.\NJump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.69,0:29:04.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"一不做.\N二不休."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.02,0:29:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Hear the other side.\NSee the other side.''
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.53,0:29:05.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,圣·奥古斯汀说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.86,0:29:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St. Augustine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:08.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 咖啡?\N- 没错.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.39,0:29:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coffee?\N- You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.37,0:29:25.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有心事.\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.67,0:29:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Something's troubling you.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:28.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原意聊聊吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.45,0:29:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.62,0:29:33.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮, 我陷入了一宗\N相当复杂的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.92,0:29:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, l'm involved\Nin a fairly complicated investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.63,0:29:35.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要求我要高度集中精神.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,requiring my complete attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.81,0:29:38.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而我却花了大部分时间\N在想你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.09,0:29:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet l spend most of my time\Nthinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:41.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那滋味.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.23,0:29:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:45.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天整个上午\N在煎蛋上看到的，都是你的脸.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.76,0:29:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been seeing your face\Nin fried eggs all this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.59,0:29:50.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道么, 有人相信科学研究上说\N吸引力是化学反应.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.90,0:29:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there are those who believe\Nin a scientific basis for attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:52.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的一种主要成分.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.40,0:29:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's chemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.69,0:29:54.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.04,0:29:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.96,0:29:56.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.27,0:29:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.83,0:30:00.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很难理解的\N透彻.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.14,0:30:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to comprehend\Nwithout perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.76,0:30:02.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.08,0:30:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.68,0:30:05.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了5年\N试图去理解它.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l spent five years\Ntrying to comprehend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.87,0:30:08.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.15,0:30:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.14,0:30:11.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说真的很难.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.42,0:30:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:15.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我对你有信心,\N就我们而言, 我能明白它.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.56,0:30:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l have faith in you,\Nin us, because l understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.29,0:30:17.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常相似.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.59,0:30:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:18.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这有帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.56,0:30:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.82,0:30:21.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想太多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.16,0:30:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.83,0:30:24.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我们所观察的\N并不是大自然本身,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.13,0:30:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''What we observe\Nis not nature itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.36,0:30:28.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是大自然向我们\N暴露出质疑的方法."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.67,0:30:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but nature exposed\Nto our method of questioning.''
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.38,0:30:31.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,海森堡说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.67,0:30:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heisenberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.48,0:30:37.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们去打保龄球吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.78,0:30:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go bowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.10,0:30:39.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.38,0:30:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.85,0:30:41.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.15,0:30:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.46,0:30:43.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我教你. 很简单的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll teach you. lt's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.34,0:30:46.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 几时?\N- 今晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.66,0:30:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- When?\N- Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.49,0:31:18.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里, 加大油门.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.82,0:31:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is, step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.13,0:31:28.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克! 杰克, 停下!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.43,0:31:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack! Jack, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:40.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我原来猜想连一句再见\N都说不上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess a simple goodbye\Nwas out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.52,0:31:53.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.82,0:31:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.61,0:31:55.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.89,0:31:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.28,0:32:01.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你一定要走吗?\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.56,0:32:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you have to leave?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:03.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你什么时候会回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.60,0:32:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will you be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.69,0:32:06.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.70,0:32:09.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个处女.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.04,0:32:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:11.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.04,0:32:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.03,0:32:15.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你和我做爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.35,0:32:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to make love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.30,0:32:18.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 此时此地?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.58,0:32:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.44,0:32:21.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不有飞机嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.72,0:32:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's your jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.41,0:32:25.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那真得感谢上帝了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.69,0:32:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:33:00.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次在猫头鹰山洞\N看到那些符号是几时的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.25,0:33:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you first see\Nthe symbol in Owl Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.66,0:33:04.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能随意\N泄露那些信息的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.96,0:33:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not at liberty\Nto divulge that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.11,0:33:07.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,骗子.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.43,0:33:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:15.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些洞穴画到底有什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the cave painting mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.80,0:33:21.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能随意\N泄露那些信息的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.11,0:33:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not at liberty\Nto divulge that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.74,0:33:25.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真见鬼, 我就是喜欢有军事头脑的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, but l love the military mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.34,0:33:37.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,北卡罗莱纳州\N的首都叫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.63,0:33:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the capital\Nof North Carolina?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.57,0:33:39.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗利城.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.83,0:33:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.32,0:33:44.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我一点好处都没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.57,0:33:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fat lot of good that will do me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.72,0:33:49.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少校, 我钦佩您的刚毅.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.00,0:33:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, l admire your fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.13,0:33:51.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有时间和耐性的话,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had l had the time and patience,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.70,0:33:54.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会将这个游戏\N无了期的玩下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.01,0:33:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might continue this game\Nindefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.01,0:33:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.03,0:34:01.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我两者都没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.32,0:34:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l have neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.45,0:34:08.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,接着咯.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.52,0:34:17.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字? 劳驾了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.87,0:34:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.48,0:34:18.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰·布里格斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.14,0:34:23.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰, 在这世上\N你最害怕什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland, what do you fear most\Nin the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.42,0:34:28.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能是\N爱不够.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.71,0:34:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility\Nthat love is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:32.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 加兰, 行行好吧, 我都快哭了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.81,0:34:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Garland, please, l shall weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.58,0:34:34.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子体重多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does your wife weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.37,0:34:37.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,115磅.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.65,0:34:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred and fifteen pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.46,0:34:40.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不错嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.82,0:34:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.43,0:34:45.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 你第一次在猫头鹰山洞\N看到那幅岩石雕刻是几时的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.76,0:34:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, when did you first see\Nthe petroglyph in Owl Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.45,0:34:48.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在-- 在梦里.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.76,0:34:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln-- ln dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:51.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.73,0:34:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.17,0:34:56.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我那晚正和库珀探员\N在钓鱼.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.44,0:34:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was night fishing\Nwith Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.36,0:35:01.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一束关,\N从远处射来.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:35:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a light,\Nguardian beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.98,0:35:06.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我被掳走了, 但我记得...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was taken, but my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.91,0:35:09.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还认得那些符号.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.25,0:35:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still l recognized the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.83,0:35:13.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些符号是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.16,0:35:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do the signs mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:19.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,某一天,\N当木星和土星相遇时,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.96,0:35:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a time,\Nif Jupiter and Saturn meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.74,0:35:22.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会来接你.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.03,0:35:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they will receive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.90,0:35:33.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰, 加兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.24,0:35:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland, Garland.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.43,0:35:39.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰, 加兰, 我原想着\N这会是一次漫长的对话呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.75,0:35:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland, Garland, l was hoping\Nfor a lengthy conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.45,0:35:42.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 扶少校上床.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.75,0:35:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, put the major to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.20,0:35:46.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他的脑袋\N已经开始迷糊了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.49,0:35:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid his mind\Nhas begun to wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:52.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,某一天,\N如果木星和土星相遇时.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.96,0:35:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a time,\Nif Jupiter and Saturn meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:36:00.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的女仆人, 琼斯,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.47,0:36:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His woman servant, Jones,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:03.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在他死后不久\N就把这个送来给我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,delivered this to me\Nshortly after he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.75,0:36:05.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃卡最后的遗物.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eckhardt's last bequest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.63,0:36:09.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个聪明的玩笑, 也许吧,\N又或是些有价值的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.94,0:36:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clever jape, perhaps,\Nor something of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.99,0:36:11.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,试试这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.28,0:36:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.95,0:36:18.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 你看, 每一个盒子\N都有打开的秘诀.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.25,0:36:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see, there's a secret\Nto opening each of these boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.54,0:36:23.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个\N快让我抓狂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.86,0:36:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this one\Nis about to drive me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.38,0:36:25.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀, 安德鲁,\N给我说点好听的吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.73,0:36:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Andrew,\Ntell me something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:31.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从巴黎到北京的外国投资者\N已经在磨拳擦掌，都等得不耐烦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.30,0:36:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our foreign investors are chomping\Nat the bit from Paris to Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.28,0:36:32.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会拥有自己的高尔夫球场了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get your golf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:35.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就建在大北方酒店\N的旁边.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right next to\NThe Great Northern Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.51,0:36:38.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那本杰明会尽一切所能\N来阻止我们的.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.81,0:36:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Benjamin is doing everything\Nhe can to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.69,0:36:41.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 为时已晚了. 他当时还在运作\N这个项目的时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.98,0:36:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's too late. When the project\Nwas still in his possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.97,0:36:43.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就已经把一切可能的障碍都给清除了:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.25,0:36:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben cleared every possible hurdle:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.93,0:36:47.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,分区, 环境影响报告书.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.18,0:36:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zoning, the impact statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.24,0:36:52.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是他自己\N最大的敌人.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.55,0:36:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was and is\Nhis own worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.70,0:36:54.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一向如此. 你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.66,0:36:58.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没干嘛, 凯萨琳, 只不过试试\N几个简单的组合.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.96,0:36:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, Catherine, l'm just trying\Na few simple combinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.67,0:37:01.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我来, 我来.\N- 别闹, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.96,0:37:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let me, let me.\N- No, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:05.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃卡的生日.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.80,0:37:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eckhardt's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.71,0:37:12.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.01,0:37:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.82,0:37:18.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这礼物到达那天的日期.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.15,0:37:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day the gift arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.06,0:37:25.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把它给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.39,0:37:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:33.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦, 真无聊.\N- 我打开的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.03,0:37:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, what a bore.\N- l opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.08,0:37:44.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.41,0:37:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrew...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.73,0:38:49.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个，我完全没有任何心理准备.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.01,0:38:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not completely prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.09,0:38:53.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就想着这是相拥着在散步就行了,\N行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.38,0:38:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a walking embrace,\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.80,0:38:58.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个人步调\N一致.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.08,0:38:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people stepping\Nas one would step.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:02.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 目前为止, 感觉还行.\N- 现在, 跟着我就行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.75,0:39:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So far, so good.\N- Now, just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.22,0:39:05.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们互相跟步.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.52,0:39:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll follow each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.02,0:39:09.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.33,0:39:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一些残留的记忆.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.60,0:39:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's genetic memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.99,0:39:14.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以前见过爸妈跳林迪舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.30,0:39:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Dad danced the lindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.53,0:39:20.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你掌握了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.80,0:39:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.56,0:39:29.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你身体靠着我的感觉真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.91,0:39:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body feels nice against mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.79,0:39:33.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得是.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.12,0:39:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was just thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.49,0:39:36.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听着, 我是否太急进了点--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.82,0:39:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if l'm being too forward--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.16,0:39:41.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 除了你的吻，我还想要更多.\N- 例如?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.46,0:39:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l want more than your kisses.\N- For instance?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.35,0:39:42.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要--\N- 这东西开了?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.63,0:39:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l want--\N- This thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.01,0:39:50.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临今晚的\N选美节决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.30,0:39:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to this final night\Nof festivities
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.42,0:39:56.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝双峰小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.74,0:39:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,celebrating the Miss Twin Peaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.31,0:40:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你们--\N这该死的, 这鬼东西到底开了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.64,0:40:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As some of you--\NDamnation, is this damn thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.34,0:40:09.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是\N我明白你为何犹豫不决了,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.65,0:40:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What l mean is\Nl understand why you hesitate,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.40,0:40:11.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么无微不至的关怀我.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why you treat me with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.97,0:40:14.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了派生出\N圣经章节和祈祷者,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.22,0:40:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The convent evokes the image\Nof helpless women,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.07,0:40:16.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,修道院还唤起了我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.36,0:40:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fearful of the thought of any emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.86,0:40:21.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对无依无靠女人们的影像，\N对所有感情都产生恐惧.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other than those derived\Nfrom scripture and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.57,0:40:25.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但当你抱着我,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.90,0:40:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you hold me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.58,0:40:27.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们接吻,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.87,0:40:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.89,0:40:31.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到安全和充满了渴望.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.21,0:40:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel safe and eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.56,0:40:34.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.05,0:40:39.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你令我产生了\N所有感觉和冲动.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.35,0:40:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of anything\Nthat you make me feel or want.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.39,0:40:49.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这开了吗? 这开了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.72,0:40:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this on? ls this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.92,0:40:51.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始有点烦他\N这样搅和了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.23,0:40:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm beginning to tire\Nof his interruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:54.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欢迎来到...\N- 我不知道. 我觉得他挺可爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Welcome to...\N- l don't know. l think he's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.28,0:40:57.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...今晚的决赛晚会...\N- 你觉得可爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.60,0:40:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...this final night of festivities...\N- You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.91,0:41:00.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想或许\N我还是会参赛的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:41:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that maybe\Nl will enter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.09,0:41:03.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 双峰小姐选美比赛?\N- 何妨呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.37,0:41:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The Miss Twin Peaks contest?\N- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.14,0:41:07.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"一不做.\N二不休."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.41,0:41:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Hear the other side.\NSee the other side.''
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:10.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么比参加双峰小姐\N更合适去开始新生活的地方吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.75,0:41:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's worse places to start\Nthan Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.56,0:41:12.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就像是一个童话故事.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.88,0:41:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's like a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.69,0:41:14.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是女王.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.02,0:41:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.36,0:41:31.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}别.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.63,0:41:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.04,0:42:19.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是活受罪.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.32,0:42:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a gyp.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.53,0:42:21.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终于遇到了你的梦中情人,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.82,0:42:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally meet the man of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.23,0:42:23.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而下一刻, 没想到吧，\N他却已经上了巴西的飞机.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.49,0:42:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,next thing l know,\Nhe's on a plane to Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.03,0:42:27.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天他会回来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.32,0:42:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.03,0:42:31.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他答应过的.\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.36,0:42:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He promised.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.48,0:42:36.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 他还答应过带我去钓鱼\N而我们始终没去成.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.80,0:42:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he also promised\Nto take me fishing and we never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.72,0:42:39.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱真让人讨厌.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.00,0:42:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.20,0:42:42.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 钓鱼?\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.50,0:42:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fishing?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.60,0:42:44.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去珍珠湖之类的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.91,0:42:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl Lake or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.14,0:42:48.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是有些钓鱼工具在货车上.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.41,0:42:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have some tackle in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.80,0:42:51.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.11,0:42:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.38,0:42:58.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 治疗伤心的方法\N有很多,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.65,0:42:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, there are many cures\Nfor a broken heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.57,0:43:04.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但却没有多少机会能见到\N鳟鱼在月光下跃龙门哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.89,0:43:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing quite like\Na trout's leap in the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.55,0:43:09.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,钓鱼去?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.83,0:43:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May l?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.49,0:43:15.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.74,0:43:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.49,0:43:29.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}木星和土星相遇{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.78,0:43:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter and Saturn meet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.54,0:43:33.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}噢, 干麦大丰收{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.85,0:43:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a crop of mummy wheat
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.43,0:43:39.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的语无伦次少校所说的行星\N不单只是远程天体.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.73,0:43:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planets our babbling major\Nspoke of are more than distant orbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.49,0:43:41.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是, 其实, 是一个锺.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.76,0:43:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are, in fact, a clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.67,0:43:43.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个会报时的锺.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.97,0:43:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clock that tells the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.72,0:43:45.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而时间...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.04,0:43:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.16,0:43:48.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,随着滴答声\N越拉越近.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.47,0:43:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time draws nearer\Nwith each ticking tock.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.95,0:43:51.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔说的没错. 那幅洞穴壁画\N是一张加入族群的请柬,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.27,0:43:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dale wasn't far wrong. The cave\Npainting is an invitation of sorts,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.18,0:43:54.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,告知我们何时开始狂欢.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,telling us when the revels begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.28,0:43:58.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但戴尔不知道\N在哪里可以找到它.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.58,0:43:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what Dale doesn't know\Nis where to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.29,0:44:02.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因此, 你看, 这洞穴壁画\N不仅是一张请柬,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.58,0:44:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For, you see, the cave painting\Nis not only an invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.48,0:44:04.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它还是一张地图.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.75,0:44:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is also a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.79,0:44:06.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一张通往守夜门的地图!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.06,0:44:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map to the Black Lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.46,0:44:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些不对劲.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.77,0:44:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.30,0:44:29.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不对.\N这儿肯定有点不对劲.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.58,0:44:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right.\NThere's something wrong here.
